short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e: No sign-up required. Works with Amazon UK/US. Stop waiting for the best price alerts, get the best offers instantly while shopping.
short.de: Keine Anmeldung nötig. Arbeitet mit Amazon DE. Kein Warten mehr auf den Bestpreis-Alarm, die besten Angebote sofort beim Shoppen.
short.es: No se necesita registro. Compatible con Amazon ES. No esperes las mejores alertas de precios, consíguelas al instante.
short.fr: Aucun abonnement requis. Fonctionne sur Amazon FR. Dorénavant, obtenez immédiatement les meilleurs prix en faisant votre shopping.
short.it: Senza registrazione. Funziona con Amazon IT. Non aspettare gli avvisi dei prezzi migliori, ottieni le offerte durante l'acquisto.
short.nl: Aanmelden niet nodig. Werkt met Amazon DE. Niet meer wachten op besteprijsmeldingen, maar de beste aanbiedingen tijdens het shoppen.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
Fetchee scans all Amazon seller listings and finds those who offer the same product. It collects prices, ratings, Prime status, delivery terms, and displays a notification with a comparison table when a better offer is available.

Supported and localized sites:
- Amazon United Kingdom (amazon.co.uk)
- Amazon Germany (amazon.de)
- Amazon France (amazon.fr)
- Amazon Italy (amazon.it)
- Amazon Spain (amazon.es)
- Amazon Netherlands (amazon.nl)

By using this application you agree to Terms Of Service, published at https://fetch.ee/en/tos
